{{term|term=Walkover}}
{{defn|defn= Race with only one horse going to the post.<ref name="equibase defs"/>  As a result, the sole starter needs only to gallop the distance of the race to be the official winner, but covering the distance is required by racing rules.<ref name="DRF terms" />}}

